<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Updated Confirmation: Your New Appointment with Krost</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f4f6; padding:24px 12px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:970px; background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">
  <!-- Body -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:24px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height: 1.6; color:#374151;">

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        Hi <strong>{{ client_firstname|default(client_name|default('Customer')) }}</strong>,
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        This email confirms that your appointment has been successfully rescheduled. We have updated our calendar to reflect your new time.
      </p>

      <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.6;">Your New Appointment Details:</p>

      <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:30px; font-size:16px line-height:1.7" >
        <li style="line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Date:</strong> {{ appointment_date|default('16/05/2026') }}</li>
        <li style="line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Time:</strong> {{ appointment_time|default('4:30 pm - 5:00 pm') }} [{{ time_zone|default('AEST (GMT+10:00) Time in Sydney NSW') }}]</li>
        <li style="line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Platform:</strong> <a href="{{ meeting_link|default('#') }}" style="color:#255793; text-decoration:underline;">{{ meeting_label|default('Online Link') }}</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin:20px 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        We have attached a calendar invitation to this email so you can easily add this to your schedule.
      </p>

      <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.6;">What happens next?</p>

      <p style="margin:0px 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        A member of the Krost Team has been allocated to your request and will be ready to assist you at the time above.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        If you have specific projects to discuss, feel free to reply to this email or if you need to make changes, you can
        <a href="{{ reschedule_link|default('#') }}" style="color:#255793; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline;">Reschedule</a>
        or
        <a href="{{ cancel_link|default('#') }}" style="color:#255793; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline;">Cancel your booking</a> here.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height: 1.6; color:#374151;">
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;">Best regards,</p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>The Krost Team</strong></p>
    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
